    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car has been pampered since day one and honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in pristine shape inside and out\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. You\u2019ve gotta see it to believe how gorgeous it is!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-Division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced dual-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This specimen has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, addressing all platform-specific weak points. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, with factory-spec suspension geometry and flawless bushing integrity. Finished in showroom-quality paint with a pristine interior, this vehicle offers the tactile engagement and linear power delivery that defines the golden era of naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Clean title.",
      "price": 43000.0,
