    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating that ensures water beads off effortlessly; there are zero stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule, still carrying that new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery is taut and supple, free from any bolster wear or creasing, while the high-gloss wood trim and digital displays remain scratch-free. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line, with every service performed ahead of schedule at an authorized dealership\u2014full documentation included. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its model. It has never seen inclement weather and has been driven only on fair-weather weekends. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a truly flawless example.",
